      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（NEXT VENUSグランプリ、歴代の優勝者を）\n（一堂に集めて祭典が行われることになった）",
      "startTime": 4.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（星見プロからは、月ストとサニピが出演する）\n（……そして、うちの優勝経験者といえばもう一人……）",
      "startTime": 11.5666666348,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "お断りします",
      "startTime": 16.4999994595,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "いや、話くらい最後まで聞いて下さいよ……",
      "startTime": 18.2666673978,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "mihoさんもスリクスを結成する前に……\nSundanceとしてグランプリで優勝してますよね",
      "startTime": 24.3666673978,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "……私の前のグループをご存じだったんですね",
      "startTime": 27.9000020027,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そりゃ知ってますよ。俺はマネージャーですよ",
      "startTime": 31.3333362262,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（Sundanceは、藤代葉さんとの二人組で）\n（BIG4にも迫ろうかという人気ユニットだった）",
      "startTime": 38.633338515,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（しかし人気絶頂期に活動休止）\n（その後、mihoさんはⅢXを結成したわけだが……）",
      "startTime": 45.4000036557,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "……昔のことですよ",
      "startTime": 49.9666693051,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "どうでしょう、先方もmihoさんに\nぜひ出てほしいとおっしゃってますし",
      "startTime": 54.6000036556,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "お断りします\n今、スリクスは新曲リリースの準備で忙しいんです",
      "startTime": 58.6666749,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "ライブでのお披露目に、MVの撮影も控えてますし\nそこに余計な仕事を入れる余裕はありません",
      "startTime": 66.1000082333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "貴方もマネージャーでしょう\n担当アイドルの仕事の予定をご存じのはずですが？",
      "startTime": 71.5333405494,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "……それに、Sundanceを知っているなら\nあのグループはもう終わったこともご存じのはず",
      "startTime": 78.9333395321,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9099.996344299996,
          "startTime": 88.0333358764
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "話はそれだけですか？\n……では、私はこれで失礼します",
      "startTime": 84.8333385149,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（mihoさんの言うことはもっともだけど）\n（でも、せっかくの機会なのに、もったいないよな……）",
      "startTime": 92.8333374976,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5233.3292643999985,
          "startTime": 98.066666762
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
