      "text": "……お疲れ様です",
      "startTime": 99.4666703223,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "ずっと練習してたんですか？\n少し休憩したらどうですか、これスポーツドリンクです",
      "startTime": 103.1666698137,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-mhk010.m4a",
      "text": "はあ……ありがとうございます",
      "startTime": 107.7333364803,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "ところで、先日の祭典なんですけど\n俺としては、決して悪い話じゃないと思うんですが……",
      "startTime": 114.1999990779,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9133.333746600001,
          "startTime": 123.3333328245
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-mhk011.m4a",
      "text": "その話は先日、お断りしたはずです\n失礼します、ロッカーから資料を取って来るので",
      "startTime": 121.2333324113,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "あ、ちょっ……\nはぁ……ろくに話も聞いてもらえないか",
      "startTime": 127.4666723567,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gaya-01.m4a",
