      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-mhk014.m4a",
      "text": "軽く一杯だけですよ\nkanaがわがまま放題するので、今日はもう疲れて",
      "startTime": 162.8333329199,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "あはは……\n少しの間だけ、ご一緒しても？",
      "startTime": 168.5333329199,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
